我们不需要知道他在哪里
we don't need to know where he is.

88
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,430
-不需要吗  -因为我们知道一件
- Oh, we don't? - Because we know something.

89
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:06,520
别人都不知道的事
Something nobody else does.

90
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,330
我们知道瓶子藏在哪
We know where the bottle is hidden.

91
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:11,820
看来你不知道"我们"这词是什么意思
I'm not sure you're clear on what the word "We" means.

92
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:15,070
