doesn't that make Cyrus my genie?

108
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:50,480
看来我只得相信你了
I guess I'll just have to trust you.

109
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:52,710
那好吧
Right then.

110
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:54,670
我们去哪找这瓶子
Where do we find this bottle?

111
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,690
我们把它埋在了高耸弦树的
We buried it in the Mimsy Meadows,

112
00:05:56,710 --> 00:05:58,350
密草地下
under the towering TumTum Tree.

113
