要是你知道他在哪  那他也一定知道你在哪
If you know where he is, surely he knows where you are, too.

190
00:09:49,970 --> 00:09:51,500
他不联系我唯一的理由
The only reason he hasn't contacted me

191
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:53,110
就是他有麻烦了
is because he must be in trouble.

192
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:54,880
所以我们得抓紧
That's why we need to pick up the pace.

193
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:57,870
也许他已经重新开始了
Or he's moved on.

194
00:09:58,190 --> 00:10:01,000
不可能  我和塞勒斯之间...
Not a chance. What Cyrus and I have--

195
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:04,160
说了你也不明白
Well, you wouldn't understand.

196
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:08,200
是啊  我是不明白
No. I suppose I wouldn't.

197
00:10:10,710 --> 00:10:12,740
没什么能阻挡我们在一起
Nothing will get in the way of us being together.

198
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,260
除了这个
Except possibly this.

199
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:36,830
用力
Harder.

200
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:39,730
再用力
Harder.

201
00:10:39,930 --> 00:10:41,010
用力
Harder!

202
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,550
兔子
Bunny!

203
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:50,000
有什么消息
What news do you have for me?

204
00:10:50,010 --> 00:10:52,790
一切都如您所料  按部就班地进行着
Everything is moving along as you predicted.

205
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:55,700
他们今早离开  去找精灵的瓶子了
They left this morning to get the genie's bottle.

206
00:10:56,290 --> 00:10:58,070
那你知道瓶子在哪了
So you know where it is then.

207
00:10:58,070 --> 00:11:00,290
我...
Uh, I, uh...

208
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:05,780
要我提醒你欺骗我的后果吗
Need I remind you of the consequences if you lie to me?

209
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:09,640
不用了  我知道瓶子在哪
Uh, no. Uh... I know exactly where it is.

210
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:18,240
我们应该能游过去
I suppose we could swim across.

211
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,330
不行
No, we can't.

212
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:21,710
要是你担心水下有什么危险
If you're afraid of dangers

213
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:23,230
我可以处理...
lurking beneath the surface, I can handle--

214
00:11:23,230 --> 00:11:24,340
我不会游泳
I can't swim.

215
00:11:25,970 --> 00:11:28,090
你怎么可能这辈子都没...
How have you lived your whole life and never--

216
00:11:28,090 --> 00:11:30,160
-我在忙其它事  -比如呢
- I was doing other things. - Like what?

217
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:32,590
比如怕水  爱丽丝
Like being afraid of water, Alice.

218
00:11:36,330 --> 00:11:39,040
好吧  那我们等摆渡吧
Fine. We'll just have to wait for the ferry.

219
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:42,350
有个更好的主意  走过去
Or--better idea-- we walk...

220
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,740
绕道而行
We walk around it.

221
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:46,130
绕过整个湖
Walk around the entire thing?

222
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:48,970
那至少要花两天
That would take two days at least.

223
00:11:50,290 --> 00:11:51,770
我们摆渡过去
We're taking the ferry.

224
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,110
她来了
There she is.

225
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:22,120
在这儿呢  仙女
Over here, fairy.

226
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:35,090
我是水仙子  你们要...
I am the Fairy Silvermist. Where may I...

227
00:12:36,230 --> 00:12:37,040
我...
I...

228
00:12:37,590 --> 00:12:38,770
你好啊  小水
Hey, Silv.

229
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:40,870
最近怎么样
How's it going?

230
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:44,410
-好了  -你俩  认识吧
- There it is. - I take it you two... know each other.

231
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:47,460
你还敢在仙境露面啊
Awfully bold of you to show your face in wonderland.

232
00:12:47,830 --> 00:12:49,400
你知道有多少人在找你吗
Do you know how many people are looking for you?

233
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:51,770
好不如去数数有多少人不在找我
Might be easier to figure out how many aren't.

234
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:52,740
很好笑吗
You think you're funny?

235
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:54,970
我认为  不管我现在说什么都没用
I think I'm buggered no matter what I say right now.

236
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:57,180
也许你俩可以在
Perhaps you two might continue reminiscing

237
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:59,020
我们渡河的时候再叙旧
while we make our way across the lake.

238
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:00,570
看来我们只能走过去了
I think we have to walk.

239
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:04,470
不  我很乐意送你们过去
Not at all. I'm happy to take you.

240
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:07,020
我们俩吗  真的吗
The both of us? Are you sure?

241
00:13:07,050 --> 00:13:09,800
当然  这是我的职责  我很专业
Of course. It's my job, and I'm a professional.

242
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:11,710
不会让私人感情影响工作
I don't let feelings get in the way of my work,

243
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:14,670
尤其是那些早已不上心的旧感情
especially old feelings that I've completely moved on from.

244
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:17,750
好吧  非常感谢
Okay. Thank you very much.

245
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:22,800
是啊  非常感谢
Yeah, thank you very much.

246
00:13:23,490 --> 00:13:24,820
非常好  我们要去
Excellent. Well, then we need to

247
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:27,180
高耸弦树下的密草地
get to The Tumtum Tree in Mimsy Meadows.

248
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,980
干嘛  我要告诉她我们的去向
What? I need to tell her where we're going.

249
00:13:31,210 --> 00:13:33,030
别担心  你可以相信我
Don't worry. You can trust me.

250
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:34,380
我是来帮忙的
I'm here to help.

251
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:49,290
你被棒子打到的烙印
That burn you got from the bars--

252
00:13:49,610 --> 00:13:51,060
我现在开始明白
I'm starting to understand

253
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:53,760
为什么只有你的笼子是用银制成的
why yours is the only cage made of silver.

254
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:56,550
是为了防止你逃跑吗
Is that to keep you from escaping?

255
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:59,480
是为了杜绝我有逃跑的想法
It's to keep me from even thinking of escaping.

256
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:03,430
精灵和银器  我们很不合
Genies and silver-- we don't mix.

257
00:14:03,810 --> 00:14:06,880
也许我们可以让你忘却痛苦
Perhaps we can take your mind off the pain.

258
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:10,450
上次下的是
Last move

259
00:14:11,330 --> 00:14:13,270
车上D3
was rook to D3.

260
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:16,960
老人家抱歉  我今天不能和你玩
Sorry, old man. I can't play with you today.

261
00:14:19,410 --> 00:14:21,230
你还有更重要的事做吗
You have something better to do?

262
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:26,640
是的
Yes.

263
00:14:28,780 --> 00:14:31,420
还真的有
Actually... I do.

264
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:48,550
我亲爱的小姐  你的愿望就是我的愿望
Mistress mine, my will is thine.

265
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:51,700
打开你的手
Open your hand.

266
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:55,370
-什么  -你的手  打开看看
- What? - Your hand. Open it.

267
00:14:58,420 --> 00:14:59,450
这些是什么
What are these?

268
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,030
它们是你的愿望
They're your wishes.

269
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,630
好漂亮
Ah, they're so pretty.

270
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:04,810
你也很漂亮
As are you.

271
00:15:06,730 --> 00:15:07,480
忘记我了吗
Forget about me?

272
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,530
抱歉  兔子
Oh. Sorry, Rabbit.

273
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:14,660
没有不舒服吧
No hard feelings?

274
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:16,870
没有  都是我的错
No, I suppose it's my fault.

275
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:19,210
我从一开始就不该把你带来
I never should have led you down here in the first place.

276
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:21,340
现在你惹了一身麻烦
It's been nothing but trouble for you.

277
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:23,760
你没把我丢在这  是我跟着你来的
You didn't leave me here. I followed you.

278
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,920
你一直是个好奇心强的女孩
You always were a curious girl.

279
00:15:26,170 --> 00:15:27,510
爱丽丝  祝你好运
Good luck, Alice.

280
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,440
那现在怎么办
So what happens now?

281
00:15:33,470 --> 00:15:34,400
任何愿望
Anything.

282
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:35,750
一切愿望
Everything.

283
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:38,470
我能许下任何愿望吗
So I can wish for anything I want?

284
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:40,710
有几个限制条件
There are a few restrictions.

285
00:15:40,710 --> 00:15:42,370
可以说是魔法的法则
The laws of magic, as it were.

286
00:15:42,370 --> 00:15:44,050
-魔法的法则  -是
- Laws of magic? - Yes.

287
00:15:44,050 --> 00:15:46,690
有四条  我不能杀人
There are four of them. I can't kill anyone.

288
00:15:46,690 --> 00:15:48,310
不能让死人复生
I can't bring anything back from the dead.

289
00:15:48,310 --> 00:15:49,790
不能改变历史
I can't change the past.

290
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:52,170
也不能让任何人坠入爱河
And I can't make anyone fall in love.

291
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,400
合情合理
Reasonable enough.

292
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:59,290
第三个愿望之后会怎么样
After the third wish, what happens then?

293
00:15:59,890 --> 00:16:01,250
我回到瓶子里
I get returned to my bottle,

294
00:16:01,250 --> 00:16:02,890
然后其他人再次找到我
and then someone else finds me.

295
00:16:02,890 --> 00:16:04,370
所以你的一生
So you spend your entire life--

296
00:16:04,370 --> 00:16:06,230
就是为主人享乐而存在
Serving at the pleasure of my masters.

297
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:07,860
是的
Yes.

298
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:15,860
如果我希望
What if I wish...

299
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,630
你能得到自由呢
for your freedom?

300
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:19,090
已经试过了
I-it's been tried,

301
00:16:19,910 --> 00:16:22,420
结果却是两败俱伤
and it's never gone well for either party.

302
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:24,290
愿望总是要付出代价的  爱丽丝
Wishes come with a cost, Alice.

303
00:16:24,290 --> 00:16:26,980
许下的愿望越大  承受的后果就越大
The bigger the wish, the greater the consequence.

304
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,460
听起来很危险
Sounds dangerous.

305
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:33,110
我觉得  你就是喜欢带点危险感的东西
I get the feeling you like a little danger.

306
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,030
你还不知道要许下什么愿望
You're still not sure what to wish for.

307
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,390
也许我们可以
Perhaps we could...

308
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,620
走一走
take a walk.

309
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:42,880
我可以给你些建议
I can give you some suggestions.

310
00:16:43,330 --> 00:16:44,850
非常乐意
I'd like that very much.

311
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:05,400
我不得不承认  我喜欢在天上飞
I must admit, I do enjoy the flying.

312
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,520
你一直喜欢飞
You always did.

313
00:17:08,710 --> 00:17:09,950
不论如何  小水
For what it's worth, Sil,

314
00:17:10,650 --> 00:17:12,470
其他的事我也喜欢
I enjoyed some of the other bits as well.

315
00:17:17,610 --> 00:17:20,350
比不上我现在要享受的
Not nearly as much as I'm going to enjoy this.

316
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:22,280
威尔
Will!

317
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:27,660
我盼这一天已经很久了
I can't tell you how long I've been waiting for that.

318
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:28,940
你怎么能
How could you--

319
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:30,190
相信我  这是他活该
Trust me. He deserved it.

320
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:32,000
可我们得去救他  他不会游泳
But we have to get him! He can't swim!

321
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,700
抱歉  不能绕路
Sorry. No detours.

322
00:17:33,700 --> 00:17:35,530
见鬼
Oh, bloody hell!

323
00:17:59,090 --> 00:17:59,950
救命
Help!

324
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,580
你对那小仙女做过什么
What did you do to that fairy?

325
00:18:17,580 --> 00:18:18,490
我对她做过什么了
What did I do to her?

326
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:19,950
她刚把我扔进这该死的湖里
She just tossed me into the bloody lake!

327
00:18:19,950 --> 00:18:21,650
显然你罪有应得
Which you clearly deserved.

328
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:24,540
现在我们困在荒无人烟的地方
Now we're stuck in the middle of nowhere,

329
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:26,320
全都怪你伤了一个小仙女的心
all because you broke a fairy's heart.

330
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:28,510
她一开始就不应该给出她的心
Well, she shouldn't have given it away in the first place.

331
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:30,630
威尔  没人能控制自己的情感
People can't help falling in love, Will.

332
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:32,330
能控制
Sure, they can.

333
00:18:32,670 --> 00:18:34,380
只要半夜偷跑出来
You just sneak out in the middle of the night,

334
00:18:34,380 --> 00:18:37,090
穿上裤子  拿上钥匙  一去不回头
grab your trousers, your keys, and don't ever look back.

335
00:18:37,100 --> 00:18:38,310
你怎么会这样
How did you get this way?

336
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:41,320
-谁这样对你了  -这与我无关  爱丽丝
- Who did this to you? - This isn't about me, Alice.

337
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:43,080
就算是  我也是坐在家里
If it were, I'd be sat back at home,

338
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:44,400
开心地看着电视
happily watching the telly.

339
00:18:45,130 --> 00:18:46,060
别问了
Don't ask.

340
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:48,940
我想告诉你的是
Look, all I'm trying to tell you is,

341
00:18:48,940 --> 00:18:50,840
你的脑中记录着对塞勒斯的记忆
you've got this picture of Cyrus in your mind,

342
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:53,470
都是一些美好细致的小回忆
these perfect little memories of how things were.

343
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:55,340
但也许那只是你一厢情愿
But maybe that's just how they were for you.

344
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:57,780
不是这样的
It wasn't like that.

345
00:18:58,930 --> 00:19:00,440
而且如果你真这么认为
And if you really believe that,

346
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,870
那我们来这干嘛
what are we doing here?

347
00:19:01,870 --> 00:19:04,240
这是你的任务  爱丽丝  不是我的
This is your quest, Alice, not mine.

348
00:19:04,780 --> 00:19:05,950
我是冲着愿望来的
I'm in it for the wish,

349
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:08,350
就和别的那些寻找精灵的人一样
just like everybody else looking for a genie.

350
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:18,310
有什么事吗
Is something wrong?

351
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,590
你看起来有些紧张
You seem a little on edge.

352
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:21,320
抱歉
Sorry.

353
00:19:22,590 --> 00:19:25,250
做精灵就如同通缉犯似的
Being a genie is a lot like being a wanted man.

354
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:27,170
总是有人在找你
Someone's always after you.

355
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:34,650
你知道是谁在找你吗
Do you know who that "someone" is?

356
00:19:38,340 --> 00:19:40,150
目前有个叫贾法尔的人
At the moment, a man called Jafar.

357
00:19:40,610 --> 00:19:42,650
他带着一根蛇头魔杖
He carries this staff with the head of a serpent.

358
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:43,930
如果你看见他
If you ever see him...

359
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:45,970
怎么了
What?

360
00:19:46,810 --> 00:19:48,240
希望你永远不要遇见他
Well, let's just hope you never do.

361
00:19:49,350 --> 00:19:50,720
他想要什么
What does he want with you?

362
00:19:51,410 --> 00:19:52,790
所有人梦寐以求
What everyone wants.

363
00:19:53,470 --> 00:19:54,660
却得不到的
What they don't have.

364
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:58,720
你不必因为我而留在外面
You don't have to stay out here on my account.

365
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:00,510
如果你在瓶子里更安全  那你该...
If you're safe in your bottle, you should--

366
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:02,940
不  我很长时间
No. This is the closest thing

367
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:04,870
没有这么接近自由了
I've had to freedom in a long time.

368
00:20:06,100 --> 00:20:07,340
我也一样
I could say the same.

369
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:10,260
如果你的家就像个囚牢
If your home is such a prison,

370
00:20:10,260 --> 00:20:11,780
为什么你还要回去
why make it your mission to return?

371
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,140
我没别的地方可去了
I have nowhere else to go.

372
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:18,500
这世界每个角落你都可以去  爱丽丝
You have the whole world, Alice.

373
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:19,760
我可以带你去
I can show it to you.

374
00:20:20,570 --> 00:20:21,900
你只要许愿就可以了
All you have to do is wish.

375
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:23,810
但我还有很多问题
But I have more questions.

376
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:25,430
你还想知道什么
What else would you like to know?

377
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:26,770
一切
Everything.

378
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:30,280
你遇见的人  你做过的事
The people you've met, the things you've done--

379
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,620
你斩杀过龙吗
